Package eu.zidek.augustin.minuscule

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MGeometricObjectPainter
    An interface for strategy that draws a given object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Canvas
    A canvas which supports easy drawing of elementary geometric objects.
    CanvasPopUpMenu
    Pop-up menu which shows on a right click on the canvas.
    GeometricObjectQueue
    Queue storing the geometric objects.
    LabelPositioningUtils
    This class has a couple of methods which are used when labels are being positioned automatically.
    MBoundingBox
    Representation of bounding rectangle, i.e.
    MCoordinate
    Lightweight immutable 2D coordinate.
    MGeometricObject
    The most general interface for all geometric objects the canvas supports.
    MinusculeWindow
    A Minuscule window that holds a canvas in it.
    MLabel
    Minuscule label with various attributes, such as position, text, color, filling and parent (a MObject to which this label is bound).
    MLabelPainter
    A Painter for MLabels.
    MLine
    Minuscule line defined by two points - the starting point and the ending point.
    MLinePainter
    A Painter for MLines.
    MPoint
    Minuscule point with various attributes such as position, radius, label, color and filling.
    MPointPainter
    A Painter for points.
    MPolygon
    Minuscule polygon.
    MPolygonPainter
    A Painter for MPolygons.
    MRectangle
    Minuscule Rectangle with various attributes such as position, size, label, circumference color, filling color, etc.
    MRectanglePainter
    A Painter for MRectangles.
    MShape
    This class serves as a wrapper for Java Shape objects.
    MShapePainter
    A Painter for MSahpe.
    PainterManager
    Painter Manager makes sure that the same geometric objects share one painter.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoPainterException
    Exception thrown when there is no registered painter for an object on the canvas.
